## EXHIBIT C — Market & Comps

### Market context

Mid-market e-commerce analytics has been growing 12–15% annually in
Europe, with 2025 showing softening as retailers tightened tech
budgets. Segment leaders include Peak (UK) and Bloomreach (US public).

Shopify launched a native analytics suite for merchants above a
certain GMV threshold in late 2025. Management notes Shopify's
offering is narrower in scope (no inventory optimization) and
primarily affects Lindstrand's smaller-end pipeline.

